OL,3,CNew Troubles legislation will address
OL,4,C'unfinished business' ` NI Secretary
OL,6,FIt comes as the Home Office revealed
OL,7,Fthere are at least 77 people in
OL,8,FEngland, almost half of which were
OL,9,Fmembers of the armed forces, whose
OL,10,Fdeaths during the Troubles remain
OL,11,Funsolved.
OL,13,FAll UK police investigations into
OL,14,FTroubles-related killings were shut
OL,15,Fdown in May last year under the
OL,16,Fprevious Conservative government's
OL,17,FLegacy Act, and a new Independent
OL,18,FCommission for Reconciliation and
OL,19,FInformation Recovery (ICRIR) was
OL,20,Festablished.
