OL,4,C'unfinished business' ` NI Secretary
OL,6,FLabour's Bill, agreed as part of a
OL,7,Fframework with the Irish Government,
OL,8,Fwill put in place a reformed Legacy
OL,9,FCommission with enhanced powers.
OL,11,FA new statutory advisory group will
OL,12,Falso be established to ensure victims
OL,13,Fand survivors of the Troubles,
OL,14,Fincluding from a service background,
OL,15,Fare heard by the Commission.
OL,17,FThe Government's plans received MPs'
OL,18,Fsupport at second reading by 320 votes
OL,19,Fto 105, majority 215.
