OL,3,CNew Troubles legislation will address
OL,4,C'unfinished business' ` NI Secretary
OL,6,FSpeaking at second reading, Mr Benn
OL,7,Fgave his assurance that "anyone who
OL,8,Fwas previously involved in
OL,9,Fparamilitary activity will not be
OL,10,Fappointed to the victims and survivors
OL,11,Fgroup".
OL,13,FHe told the Commons he had heard the
OL,14,Fcall from families and veterans, some
OL,15,Fof which looked on from Parliament's
OL,16,Fgalleries, to "get the answers that
OL,17,Fyou seek".
OL,19,F"We know that this unfinished business
OL,20,Ffalls to us, all of us, because time
OL,21,Fis running out," he added.
