OL,4,C'unfinished business' ` NI Secretary
OL,6,FThe Government is repealing an
OL,7,Fimmunity scheme which formed part of
OL,8,Fthe previous Legacy Act, but which was
OL,9,Fruled unlawful in the courts.
OL,11,F"We know that one of the principal
OL,12,Freasons for that lack of support was
OL,13,Fthe Act's attempt to offer immunity
OL,14,Ffrom prosecution, including to
OL,15,Fterrorists who had committed the most
OL,16,Fappalling murders," he said.
