OL,3,CNew Troubles legislation will address
OL,4,C'unfinished business' ` NI Secretary
OL,6,FDan Jarvis, security minister and
OL,7,Fformer member of the Parachute
OL,8,FRegiment who served in Northern
OL,9,FIreland, said: "The last government's
OL,10,FLegacy Act shut down police
OL,11,Finvestigations and proposed immunity
OL,12,Ffor terrorists.
OL,14,F"This left many families feeling they
OL,15,Fhad nowhere to go to continue their
OL,16,Fsearch for justice, or simply for
OL,17,Fanswers about what happened to their
OL,18,Floved ones.
OL,20,F"This Government's legislation will
OL,21,Fput that right."
