OL,4,C'unfinished business' ` NI Secretary
OL,6,F"The Bill before us today strips out
OL,7,Fthe conditional immunity introduced by
OL,8,Fthe Legacy Act, and it reopens the
OL,9,Fdoor to vexatious litigation against
OL,10,Fveterans, whilst leaving it very
OL,11,Funlikely that terrorists will be
OL,12,Fprosecuted."
